  "subject": "Run tests in parallel",
  "commit_message": "Run tests in parallel\n\n- one jvm per core (vs one jvm before -> single threaded)\n- sequential execution within the forks\n- fix some tests that are now executed that were not before\n- add explicit excludes for those tests that were implicitly\n  skipped previously\n\nIssue-ID: SO-4271\nChange-Id: I312aad073dc2d58edfb82c233b3282dd7ae6125a\nSigned-off-by: Fiete Ostkamp <fiete.ostkamp@telekom.de>\n",
